st_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1641877746.586958", "card_id": "Q_510949279", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 23}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "美国心脏病患者接受全球首例猪心移植，供体猪已经过基因改造，这意味着什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据海外网综合《今日美国》、美国广播公司等外媒 10 日消息，一名美国男子成为全球首位从转基因猪身上接受心脏移植的人。 这名美国男子名叫大卫·贝内特，现年 57 岁。其主治医生说，手术在美国巴尔的摩进行，时长 7 小时，目前病患状况良好。外媒称，移植手术中使用的猪已经过基因改造，但贝内特接下来的情况未知。贝内特的儿子也称，目前一切处于未知状态。 心脏移植是挽救贝内特生命的最后希望，贝内特在手术前一天也表示：「要么死，要么做移植手术。这是我最后的选择。」手术前，他已卧床六周，处于心脏病晚期，他表示「期待自己康复后能下床行动」。全球首例！美国心脏病患者接受猪心移植，修改了 10 个基因... | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-3027223917a3f8079c5b6eca0e802a66_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "135 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/510949279"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ip52G9IW27btMEAMaCDc1ODI1ODYyIOO6844GMAE4VUAccgk1MTA5NDkyNzl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1641877746.5876293", "card_id": "Q_509228302", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 85}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "计算机再过几年会没落？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e055be9cf2d49bcf955ae8e4cfc886f9_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "119 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/509228302"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ip52G9IW27btMEAMaCDc1NDQzMTM0ILjnt44GMAY4yAFAHXIJNTA5MjI4MzAyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1641877746.5881398", "card_id": "Q_508534148", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 167}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "我去峨眉山旅游峨眉山的猴子攻击我我一个左勾拳给猴子打晕了，算伤害野生动物吗?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-ac2f7ad70bfb63450642de7e25a865e4_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "114 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color"